Package: zaro
Title: Zarr via Arrow
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Low-level Zarr V3 interface built on Arrow filesystem and codec
    infrastructure. Provides direct access to Zarr stores on local filesystems,
    S3, and GCS via Arrow, with fallback to GDAL virtual filesystems for HTTP
    and other protocols via gdalraster. Supports Kerchunk JSON and Parquet
    reference stores for virtual Zarr access to existing archives.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
